{"tid":478487,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"學生持港獨標語與林鄭合照後收警告 校方：一直本著基督精神","createTime":"2017-11-24T06:19:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T13:51:16.000Z","uid":48093,"like":3,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"e29e2ced53a55a9449ce9fa7118888b78644f5c1","tid":478487,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T06:19:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171124/large/1511503463_867b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171124%2Flarge%2F1511503463_867b.png&h=465b1973&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n葵涌循道中學中五學生劉康，上周出席校園記者活動，手持港獨標語「成功爭取」與特首林鄭月娥大合照。該校校長林美儀回覆《蘋果》查詢時指，該校一直本著基督精神，發展全人教育，藉宣講福音，培育豐盛生命。<br />\n<br />\n她續指，學校着重學生的全人發展，並致力培育學生具有良好品格、明辨性思考能力及正面價值觀和態度，使他們能尊重他人，尊重場合，以及包容不同價值。學校亦有一貫的機制為有需要的學生提供輔導。校園是學習的地方，我們會繼續發揮教育專業精神，讓我們的學生在安全、有秩序及專業教學的環境下學習。"},{"pid":"c8ccf7e2099242742a8915527f9d22b8744e719a","tid":478487,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T06:21:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f1908ab6084b98bccd1c8cf93bcc740daceef95","tid":478487,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T06:23:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be53d7464a5771c44828021d63acdf9e05869e29","tid":478487,"uid":53687,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T06:26:26.000Z","msg":"奶共嘛認囉，九唔搭八"},{"pid":"e7cad196f347ca9f93df099e7c1022bfa8074793","tid":478487,"uid":38671,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T06:28:04.000Z","msg":"基督精神<br />\n你地咪做緊釘人十字架果個囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"310c6632b1dfefc2ea4f9d7b4aa9ccfc1963aa05","tid":478487,"uid":91633,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T06:29:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>基督精神<br />\n你地咪做緊釘人十字架果個囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"